    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, so my neighbor just changed their wifi name to \"WE SEE YOU IN THE KITCHEN\" and i'm actually getting really creeped out. like i literally just walked in there to get a snack and it pops up. is this like a thing people do to mess with others or is it more specific? it feels like they're watching me.",
