    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even just the name though. every time i move from the living room to the kitchen, the signal strength on my phone spikes like crazy, almost like it's tracking where i am. do you think they have some kind of sensor setup or something to do that? it feels way too targeted to be a coincidence.",
